5️⃣ Set Permissions

Assuming your Docker containers run as PUID=1000 / PGID=1000 (your user craig):

sudo chown -R craig:craig ~/appdata
sudo chown -R craig:craig /mnt/storage
sudo chmod -R 775 ~/appdata /mnt/storage
